body:
The following query uses the `text` operator to search the `plot`
field in the `movies` collection for all terms in the query string
`automobile race`.

MongoDB Search returns results based on the [Synonym](synonyms-ref) in the [properly formatted](synonyms-coll-spec), `synonymous_terms`, specified in the synonym
mapping definition of the index for the `sample_mflix.movies`
collection.

**Input:**

```json
db.movies.aggregate([
  {
    "$search": {
      "text": {
        "path": "plot",
        "query": "automobile race",
        "matchCriteria": "all",
        "synonyms": "my_synonyms"
      }
    }
  },
  {
    "$limit": 20
  },
  {
    "$project": {
      "_id": 0,
      "plot": 1,
      "title": 1,
      "score": { "$meta": "searchScore" }
    }
  }
])
```

